data.description: Come check out this sweet home in the city of Muskegon. It boasts a completely fenced in back yard and off street parking. It is move in ready and has been entirely redone in the last 2 years. Updates include: New kitchen, bath, flooring, windows, doors, walls, wiring, high efficiency furnace, water heater, light fixtures, appliances, front porch & back steps. You will enjoy 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, open concept kitchen/dining/living room, mudroom, basement laundry with lots of extra storage. Minutes away from the farmer's market, restaurants, shopping, entertainment and beaches. Possession at close. Cash, conventional, FHA, VA, MSHDA financing terms available. Call now to schedule a showing!!
